description:
Wholesalers that provide computer-related services. Such services
may include consulting on a contract or fee basis, database
development, computer maintenance and repair, tape and diskette
conversion services, and computer requirements analysis.
For wholesale distributors of computer hardware, software, and
related equipment, use MCC 5045.
